@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ncopcy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs(v2))
    v2 = 0.43
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.53) + wp.sin((tmp + 0.25 / v0 + 0.52)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.09)) / wp.sin((v2 + 0.77 - v0 + 0.34)))
    v2 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.exp(tmp + 0.85) + v1))
    v1 = wp.cos((0.96 + (v1 + 0.08 / v2 + 0.12)))
    v0 = 0.62
    data[tid] = v0
